y class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable geist_mono_8d43a2aa-module__8Li5zG__variable antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-gray-50\"><header class=\"bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-3\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-linear-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white text-sm\">⚡</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold bg-linear-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">AI 工具市场</span></div></a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"relative w-72\"><div class=\"relative\"><svg class=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-gray-400\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z\"></path></svg><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"全局搜索...\" class=\"w-full pl-9 pr-4 py-2 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all\" value=\"\"/></div></div><a class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"学院\" href=\"/learn\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">🎓</span></a><a href=\"http://hsinky.cn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg transition-colors group\" title=\"个人博客\"><span class=\"group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">📰</span></a></div></div></header><div class=\"flex\"><aside class=\"w-72 bg-white border-r border-gray-200 flex flex-col fixed left-0 top-14 h-[calc(100vh-56px)]\"><nav class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🏠</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">首页</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">概览与推荐</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/skill\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">✨</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Skill</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">可复用的能力模块</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/mcp\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔌</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">MCP</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">外部工具与服务接入</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/agent\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🤖</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Agent</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">自主决策的AI助手</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/prompt\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">📝</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Prompt</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">高效沟通的模板</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/workflow\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\">入门路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">企业级实践</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-600 to-gray-700 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">企业级实践</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">从原型到生产环境</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->60分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>入门路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/production/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/production/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/production/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>第一课：产品化的完整流程</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 border-l-4 border-slate-500 p-4 rounded-r-lg\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-2\">核心认知</h3><p class=\"text-gray-700\">从 Demo 到生产环境，不仅仅是换个服务器部署，而是一套完整的<strong>产品化流程</strong>。</p></div><div class=\"bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3\">产品化的关键差异</h4><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-red-700\">Demo 阶段</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 功能验证为主</li><li>• 硬编码配置</li><li>• 单用户测试</li><li>• 错误不处理</li></ul></div><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-green-700\">生产环境</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 稳定性第一</li><li>• 配置化部署</li><li>• 多用户并发</li><li>• 完善的监控告警</li></ul></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-700\">上线前检查清单</h4><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2\"><li>✓ 所有 Prompt 都有版本号和文档</li><li>✓ 生产环境使用独立的 API Key（非测试 Key）</li><li>✓ 配置了完善的日志和监控</li><li>✓ 设置了成本告警阈值</li><li>✓ 完成了安全审查和权限配置</li><li>✓ 有回滚方案和降级策略</li><li>✓ 已进行负载测试和压力测试</li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>第二课：成本控制与预算管理</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-orange-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-700\">为什么成本控制很重要？</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3\">大模型 API 调用成本随规模快速放大。1000 个用户每天调用 10 次，即使每次只 $0.01，月成本也会超过 $30,000。</p><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border text-xs\"><p>成本 = 用户数 × 调用频次 × 单次成本</p><p class=\"mt-1\">= 1000 × 10 × $0.01 = $100/天 = $3,000/月</p></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3\">策略 1：模型选择路由</h4><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-green-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">简单任务</span><span>→ 小模型（GPT-4o-mini, Haiku）成本降低 10-20 倍</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-blue-500 text-white px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs\">复杂任务</span><span>→ 大模型（GPT-4, Claude 3.5）确保质量</span></div></div><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2\">自动检测任务复杂度，选择合适的模型</p></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3\">策略 2：智能缓存</h4><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2\">相同输入的请求直接返回缓存结果，节省 API 调用：</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">精确缓存</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">相同输入完全匹配</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">命中率：50-70% | 节省：50%成本</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">语义缓存</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">输入相似度 &gt; 0.95 时命中</p><p class=\"text-xs text-green-600\">命中率：70-80% | 节省：70%成本</p></div></div></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold mb-3\">策略 3：预算控制与降级</h4><div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">预算告警</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">设置每日/每月预算，达到 80% 时告警，95% 时自动降级</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">降级策略</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">触发降级后，切换到小模型或返回缓存结果</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-700\">用户提示</p><p class=\"text-gray-600\">预算耗尽时，提示用户&quot;服务繁忙，请稍后再试&quot;</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">3</span>第三课：安全与合规</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-red-700\">安全是企业的生命线</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-700\">AI 应用涉及用户数据、企业机密、API 密钥，任何一个环节的漏洞都可能导致严重后果。</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-orange-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">API 密钥管理</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 生产密钥使用环境变量或密钥管理系统</li><li>• 代码中不硬编码密钥</li><li>• 为不同环境使用不同的 Key</li><li>• 定期轮换密钥</li><li>• 使用最小权限的 API Key</li></ul></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">输入验证与清洗</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 严格验证用户输入的格式和长度</li><li>• 过滤掉敏感信息后再发送给 AI</li><li>• 检测并拦截注入攻击</li><li>• 设置单次输入的最大 Token 限制</li></ul></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">输出过滤</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 敏感领域强制添加免责声明</li><li>• 过滤不当内容（仇恨、暴力、歧视）</li><li>• 验证输出格式符合预期</li><li>• 对结构化输出进行 schema 验证</li></ul></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">审计与追溯</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1\"><li>• 记录所有 AI 调用的完整日志</li><li>• 支持按用户、功能、时间范围查询</li><li>• 保存 Prompt 和输出内容用于审查</li><li>• 数据保留策略（如 90 天后删除）</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/beginner\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->入门路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[87161,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[40715,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[78691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[30470,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/stat